import React from 'react';
import styled from 'styled-components';

const LogoContainer = styled.div`
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: ${props => props.theme.spacing.sm};
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: ${props => props.theme.transitions.base};
  
  &:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }
`;

const LogoIcon = styled.div`
  width: ${props => props.size === 'large' ? '48px' : props.size === 'medium' ? '36px' : '28px'};
  height: ${props => props.size === 'large' ? '48px' : props.size === 'medium' ? '36px' : '28px'};
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
`;

const LogoText = styled.span`
  font-family: ${props => props.theme.fonts.primary};
  font-weight: ${props => props.theme.fontWeights.bold};
  font-size: ${props => props.size === 'large' ? props.theme.fontSizes['2xl'] : 
                        props.size === 'medium' ? props.theme.fontSizes.xl : 
                        props.theme.fontSizes.lg};
  background: ${props => props.theme.colors.gradientPrimary};
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
`;

const LokanexLogo = ({ size = 'medium', showText = true, ...props }) => {
  return (
    <LogoContainer {...props}>
      <LogoIcon size={size}>
        <svg
          width="100%"
          height="100%"
          viewBox="0 0 100 100"
          fill="none"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        >
          {/* Outer ring with segments */}
          <circle
            cx="50"
            cy="50"
            r="40"
            stroke="url(#ringGradient)"
            strokeWidth="3"
            fill="none"
            strokeDasharray="8,4"
            opacity="0.8"
          />
          
          {/* Inner geometric L */}
          <g transform="translate(50,50)">
            {/* Main L structure */}
            <rect x="-20" y="-20" width="8" height="40" fill="url(#lMain)" rx="2" />
            <rect x="-20" y="12" width="28" height="8" fill="url(#lMain)" rx="2" />
            
            {/* L accent elements */}
            <rect x="-15" y="-15" width="3" height="3" fill="url(#accent1)" rx="1" />
            <rect x="-5" y="15" width="3" height="3" fill="url(#accent2)" rx="1" />
            <rect x="5" y="15" width="3" height="3" fill="url(#accent3)" rx="1" />
          </g>
          
          {/* Floating particles */}
          <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="2" fill="url(#particle1)" opacity="0.7" />
          <circle cx="80" cy="25" r="1.5" fill="url(#particle2)" opacity="0.6" />
          <circle cx="25" cy="80" r="2.5" fill="url(#particle3)" opacity="0.8" />
          <circle cx="75" cy="75" r="1" fill="url(#particle4)" opacity="0.5" />
          
          {/* Connection lines */}
          <path d="M20 20 Q35 15 50 20" stroke="url(#conn1)" strokeWidth="1.5" fill="none" opacity="0.4" />
          <path d="M80 25 Q65 30 50 25" stroke="url(#conn2)" strokeWidth="1.5" fill="none" opacity="0.4" />
          <path d="M25 80 Q35 70 50 75" stroke="url(#conn3)" strokeWidth="1.5" fill="none" opacity="0.4" />
          <path d="M75 75 Q65 70 50 75" stroke="url(#conn4)" strokeWidth="1.5" fill="none" opacity="0.4" />
          
          {/* Central core */}
          <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="12" fill="url(#coreGradient)" opacity="0.3" />
          <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="6" fill="url(#coreCenter)" opacity="0.6" />
          
          {/* Corner brackets */}
          <path d="M15 15 L20 15 L20 20" stroke="url(#bracket1)" strokeWidth="2" fill="none" opacity="0.6" />
          <path d="M85 15 L80 15 L80 20" stroke="url(#bracket2)" strokeWidth="2" fill="none" opacity="0.6" />
          <path d="M15 85 L20 85 L20 80" stroke="url(#bracket3)" strokeWidth="2" fill="none" opacity="0.6" />
          <path d="M85 85 L80 85 L80 80" stroke="url(#bracket4)" strokeWidth="2" fill="none" opacity="0.6" />
          
          {/* Gradients */}
          <defs>
            <linearGradient id="ringGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="25%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="50%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="75%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="lMain" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ffffff" />
              <stop offset="30%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="70%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#0099cc" />
            </linearGradient>
            <radialGradient id="accent1" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff8c42" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="accent2" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#44a08d" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="accent3" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#0099cc" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="particle1" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff8c42" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="particle2" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#44a08d" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="particle3" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#0099cc" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="particle4" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff8c42" />
            </radialGradient>
            <linearGradient id="conn1" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="conn2" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="conn3" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="conn4" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
            </linearGradient>
            <radialGradient id="coreGradient" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" stopOpacity="0.4" />
              <stop offset="70%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" stopOpacity="0.2" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff6b35" stopOpacity="0.1" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="coreCenter" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ffffff" stopOpacity="0.8" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#00d4ff" stopOpacity="0.4" />
            </radialGradient>
            <linearGradient id="bracket1" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff8c42" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="bracket2" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#44a08d" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="bracket3" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#0099cc" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="bracket4" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff8c42" />
            </linearGradient>
          </defs>
        </svg>
      </LogoIcon>
      {showText && <LogoText size={size}>Lokanex</LogoText>}
    </LogoContainer>
  );
};

export default LokanexLogo;
